eir most active piece, consequently activating one of our least. That's a win for us, albeit a small one. } 11. Nxc6 { If White doesn't capture the bishop now they might not get another chance to do so. For instance, if White continues with } ( 11. d4 $2 Be4 12. c3 f6 { Black keeps the bishop pair and has a small advantage. } ) 11... Rxc6 $10 { [%cal Be7e6,Bg8f6,Bf8d6,Be8e7,Bh8d8][%csl Bd8][%cal Bd8c8]This endgame is a bit dry, but Black has no issues. We can continue with our typical ideas: ...Nf6, ...e6, ...Bd6, etc. } * 

