With accurate play we should be better. Black should create a bastion in the center with ...Bc6-d5 and develop. White might proceed with } 19. Bg5 Bc6 20. d5 $2 { Sacrificing a pawn to open up the central files is certainly an idea worthy of consideration. } 20... Bxd5 21. Red1 b6 22. Rac1 Qb7 { White's activity is quite remarkable, but it can accomplish little in this setting. Black is easily holding together the defense and is simply much better. } * 

