o minor pieces for a rook and White needs to play with incredible precision to avoid falling off the board. } 20. f5 { is the only move. After } 20... Nxf5 $146 { White has to spot an only move yet again } 21. Rxe6 Kxe6 22. Bd2 { once again, only move! Noticing a pattern here? } 22... Be5 23. Re1 ( 23. Bf4 Ne3 $146 24. Qh3+ f5 25. Bxe3 { dxe3 26.Qxe3 } 25... Kf6 { But finally, if White manages to see all of this the position should be a draw. } ) 23... d4 * 

