y winning move, but once we spot it it is clear that White's position is hopeless. } ) 14... Bxd1 15. Nc6+ Kf7 16. Nxd8+ Rhxd8 17. Raxd1 Nxc2 $19 { [%cal Bc2e1,Bc2a3][%csl Ra3,Re1]Black will be up an exchange for nothing. The rest should be a matter of technique. } * 

