. h3 Bxf3 { Be sure to avoid } ( 7... Bh5 $2 8. g4 Bg6 9. Ne5 $146 ) 8. Qxf3 Rc8 $10 { [%cal Ba7a6,Be7e6,Bg8f6,Yf8e7,Ye8g8,Yh8f8]White does have the bishop pair, true, but Black has no issues here. This should be roughly equal. We can continue with the typical ...a6, ...e6, ...Nf6, etc. and eventually castle with a fine position. } * 

