 a slight advantage. } ) 8... Qxd5 $10 { Recapturing with the queen is the most accurate. We want our knights to remain connected until we can land ...a6. After If White elects to keep the queens on the board, say for instance with } 9. Qxd5 exd5 { Black has decent play. We can castle queenside and repel the bishop with ...a6. } * 

